{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs72 PROVERBS

\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 On the Worth of Wisdom

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 1}The proverbs of Solomon, the son of David, king of Israel.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Aim of the Book

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}That people may learn wisdom and discipline,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and understand words of discernment;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}that they may win training in prudence,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in right and in justice and rectitude;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}that shrewdness be imparted to the simple,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and knowledge and insight to youth \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}the wise too, who listens, will grow wiser,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the prudent more skilled in direction \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}that proverbs and parables may be plain,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
even the words of the wise and their riddles
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Motto of the Book

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Reverence for the Lord is the basis of knowledge,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but wisdom and discipline are scorned by fools.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 Exhortation and Warning

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Listen, my child, to your father\uc1\u8217*s instruction,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and do not forsake what you mother has taught you;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}they will be a garland to your head,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and a chain for your neck.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}My son, if sinners entice you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
do not consent.{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}If they say,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
\uc1\u8220*Come with us, let us lurk for the blameless,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and ambush the innocent for fun \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}let us swallow them up like the grave, alive
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and entire, just as those that go down to the pit.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}Precious wealth of all sorts will be ours,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
we will fill our houses with spoil.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}Cast your lot with us;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
we will all share what we steal,\uc1\u8221*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}Do not go their way, my child.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Keep your foot away from their path.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}For their feet hasten to evil,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and they rush to shed blood.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}The net is spread in the sight of the birds,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who hungrily take the bait.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}Their own is the blood they lurk for.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Their own are the lives they ambush.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}So end all who would grasp at gain \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
it destroys the life of its owner.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Appeal of Wisdom

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}Wisdom cries aloud in the streets,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in the squares echoes her voice,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}she calls from the top of the walls,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
at the doors of the city gates she says:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}\uc1\u8220*How long will you fools love folly,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and scoffers delight in scoffing,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and fools in their hatred of knowledge?
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}Respond to my rebuke.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
See! I speak my mind to you;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
I will tell you my thoughts.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24}Because you refused my call,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
gave no heed to my hand when it beckoned you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}rejected all my counsel,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and refused my admonition,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 26}when distress falls on you, I will laugh;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
I will mock, when your terror comes,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 27}when your terror comes as a storm,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
as a whirlwind your distress.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 28}Then I will not answer their call;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
they may seek, but they will not find me.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 29}Because they hated knowledge,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and rejected the fear of the Lord,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 30}would have nothing of my counsel.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
but despised all my admonition,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 31}they must eat the fruit of their ways,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and be filled with their own devices.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 32}By their own choice will the simple be slain.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Prosperous ease will bring fools to destruction.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 33}But he who listens to me will live securely,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in a peace unruffled by fear of calamity.\uc1\u8221*        
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Blessed Fruits of Wisdom

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 2}My child, if you welcome my words,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and hold close my commandments,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}giving heedful ear to wisdom,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and bending your mind to reason;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}if you seek to invoke understanding.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and lift up your voice to reason,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}seeking for her as if for silver,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and searching for her as if for treasure:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}then the fear of the Lord will be plain to you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the knowledge of God you will find.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}For the Lord is the giver of wisdom.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
The source of knowledge and insight.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}He stores up ability for the upright;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
he shields the blameless life.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}He guards the paths of the just,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and he watches the way of the faithful.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}Then justice and right will be plain to you;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
you will keep to all paths that are good.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}When wisdom will enter your mind,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and in knowledge you find your pleasure,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}discretion will watch over you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and understanding will guard you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}and save you from wicked ways,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
from people of perverse speech,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}who leave the paths of right,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
to walk in ways of darkness \uc1\u8211*
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}happy in doing wrong,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
exulting in wicked perverseness,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}all crooked in their paths.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and devious in their ways.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}From the adultress too, it will save you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
the sinning woman of slippery speech,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}who forsakes the partner of her youth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and forgets her bond with her God;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}for her house sinks down to death,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and her paths lead to the place of the dead.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}None that visit her ever come back,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
or arrive at the paths of life.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}Therefore walk in the way of good people.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Keep in the paths of the righteous,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}for the upright will live in the land,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the blameless alone will enjoy it;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}while bad people are cut off from it.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the faithless uprooted.
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Wisdom of Trusting and Honouring the Lord

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\cf1\f1\fs22 3}My son, do not forget my teaching,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
keep my commandments in mind;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 2}for a long and happy life
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and fulness of peace will they bring you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 3}Let not kindness and faithfulness leave you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Bind them about your neck;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 4}so favour and good repute will you find
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
alike with God and people.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 5}Trust the Lord with all your heart.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Lean not on your own understanding:
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 6}in all your ways acknowledge him,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and he will smooth your paths.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 7}Do not pride yourself on your wisdom;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
fear the Lord and turn from evil.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 8}Then there will be health to your body,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and refreshment to your bones.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 9}If you honour the Lord with your wealth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
with the first-fruits of all that comes in to you,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 10}your barns will be filled with corn,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and with wine will your vats overflow.        
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Worth of Wisdom

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 11}Reject not, my son, the Lord\uc1\u8217*s chastening.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Do not spurn His reproof.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 12}For whom the Lord loves, he chastens,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
he reproves the child he delights in.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 13}Happy those who find wisdom,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
they who obtain understanding.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 14}For she brings a gain fairer than silver,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
a revenue better than gold.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 15}More precious is she than corals,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and with her can no treasures compare.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}In her right hand is long life,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
in her left are riches and honour.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}Her ways are pleasant ways,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and all her paths are peace.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 18}She is a tree of life to those who grasp her.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Happy they who hold her fast.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 19}The Lord by wisdom founded the earth,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
by understanding established the heavens.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 20}By knowledge he broke up the deeps.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and the clouds he made drip with dew.*************
\par}

{\pard\sb360\sa360\fs32 The Security that comes from Wisdom

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 21}Observe, my child, discretion and wisdom,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
let them never out of your sight;
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 22}so will they be life to you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
An ornament round your neck.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 23}You will then go your way securely.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Without ever striking your foot.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 24}You will sit down unafraid,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and your sleep will be sweet where you lie.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 25}You will fear no sudden terror,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
nor the tempest that falls on the wicked.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 26}For the Lord is the ground of your hope.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
He will keep your foot from the snare.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 27}Withhold from your neighbour no good
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
Which you have in your power to do them.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 28}Do not tell them \uc1\u8211* when you can afford it \uc1\u8211* to go
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
and come back, with the promise of something tomorrow.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 29}Devise no mischief against your neighbour,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
while they are trustfully living beside you.
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 30}Do not idly quarrel with anyone
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
who has not done you any harm.
\par}

{\pard 

\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2440\li2800
{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 31}Do not envy the violent,
\par}

{\pard\sl280\slmult1\fs24\fi-2080\li2800
or choose any one of their ways.
\par}

